performance.info-texture: ʻOku mau fokotuʻu atu ke ʻoua naʻa toe laka hake ʻi he 256MB ʻo e vitio RAM ki he ngaahi meʻangaue toʻotoʻo. ʻOku mau toe fokotuʻu atu foki ke fakaʻaongaʻi ʻa e fotunga tuilalanga ʻo lahi ange ʻi he 2048 x 2048.
performance.info-lights: Neongo ʻoku ʻikai fakaʻata ʻa e ngaahi maama longomoʻui ʻi he ngaahi meʻangaue toʻotoʻo, ka ʻoku mau fokotuʻu atu ke ʻoua naʻa toe laka hake ʻi he maama ʻe 3 ʻi hoʻo meʻa ʻoku ke mamata ki ai (toʻo ʻa e ngaahi maama ʻo e Hemisifia) ke ke lele ʻi he tafaʻaki ki lalo ʻo e CS.
performance.info-fileSize: ʻOku mau fokotuʻu atu ha faile fakaʻosi ʻo ʻikai toe lahi ange ʻi he 16MB ki he ngaahi fehokotaki bandwidth maʻulalo. ʻE hanga ʻe hono fakasiʻisiʻi ʻo e lahi ʻo e faile ʻo fakasiʻisiʻi ʻa e taimi ʻe fie maʻu ke download ai hoʻo meʻa ʻoku fai.
